4 SYNOPSIS:
5 Under existing law, rape in the first degree,
6 sodomy in the first degree, and sexual torture are
7 Class A felonies.
8 This bill would provide that rape in the first
9 degree, sodomy in the first degree, and sexual torture
10 are capital offenses when the victim is less than 12
11 years of age.
12 This bill would also provide that a person
13 convicted of rape in the first degree, sodomy in the
14 first degree, or sexual torture and sentenced to life
15 imprisonment must serve a minimum of 30 years in prison
16 prior to being considered for parole.
